Text: Inspired by a profound desire to explore new playgrounds, Vault recently chose to acquire parcels of land in The Sandbox metaverse. Voxel by voxel, our bespoke world will become an eclectic space fostering boundary-pushing creativity.

Vault aims to embrace Web3 by delving deep into the metaverse through the creation of nonfungible tokens (NFTs). By lining our shelves with physical and digital assets from different eras, ideas hybridize and create those perfect conditions to spark new creativity for the future.

For a preview of our roadmap: #SUPERGUCCI will be Vault’s first NFT project as part of a three-part drop, beginning February 1st and featuring 10 exclusive NFTs, each accompanied by a ceramic sculpture handmade in Italy and co-designed by Gucci and @superplastic. #GucciVault

Text: For the metaverse and NFTs, there is a strong focus on Community, which sets a new tone for how people can participate and allow for more access in contrast to what was done before.
"The beauty of the virtual world is that anyone can come and join. The metaverse is a feeling, and it should be a beautiful one. Giving tools to more people allows this"
Paraphrasing: The Metaverse allows people to make a new world without the problems of the physical world. This creates a lot of opportunities for more people to have better self-expression!

There is still some clarification and learning to do in the whole industry. The term NFT will also evolve, get contextualized, and more as people outside of DeFi or "classic" crypto start adopting them.

#CryptoFashionWeek Thursday is about, Phygital, Direct-to-Avatar, and Metaverse runways! 

XR innovators like Damara Ingles, @karinnanobbs, and @CrucibleNetwork  showcase a phygital future without material and conceptual limits for fashion! 

https://t.co/5DFKohxYNC https://t.co/hvBSemhssv
